with depression.

39:54.726 --> 39:56.261
But what they didn't
know was that...

39:56.361 --> 39:59.465
That the mom knew where
the gun was hidden. Aha.

39:59.565 --> 40:02.468
And what about witness OA16?
German?

40:02.568 --> 40:05.504
Italian? Romanian?

40:05.604 --> 40:07.439
Chinese.

40:08.239 --> 40:12.511
You are very good
at this job.

40:14.446 --> 40:16.615
Yeah, I-I know.

40:16.715 --> 40:18.383
Maybe I should
just let you be

40:18.484 --> 40:20.519
who you want to be.

40:21.920 --> 40:23.722
Yeah.

40:25.323 --> 40:27.358
But there is one thing
I could do for you

40:27.459 --> 40:29.194
to help you get back
on your feet.

40:29.294 --> 40:31.863
Uh, help us both, actually.

40:31.963 --> 40:33.799
If you'll let me.

40:38.637 --> 40:41.640
It is 1:00 p.m.,
