40:41.740 --> 40:44.510
You're a detective again,
an investigator.

40:44.610 --> 40:46.144
This is what you want.

40:46.244 --> 40:48.113
This is the way back.

40:48.213 --> 40:49.447
Okay? Right.

40:49.548 --> 40:52.083
Right? Okay.
Todd?

40:52.183 --> 40:54.085
Susan.
Congratulations.

40:54.185 --> 40:56.054
I heard you were
coming aboard.

40:56.154 --> 40:57.288
Thanks.
Thank you. Yeah.

40:57.388 --> 40:58.557
Well, it's not
a permanent thing.

40:58.657 --> 40:59.825
I'm just covering
for the investigator

40:59.925 --> 41:00.992
on maternity leave.

41:01.092 --> 41:02.260
Right. Nadia.

41:02.360 --> 41:03.695
She had twins.
Yeah, yeah.

41:03.795 --> 41:06.264
And I'll be around now,
so, you know,

41:06.364 --> 41:08.233
if maybe a lunch happens...

41:08.333 --> 41:10.435
I mean, we'll be
working together,

41:10.536 --> 41:12.738
and you'll need me.

41:12.838 --> 41:14.039
Professionally.

41:14.139 --> 41:16.441
Okay, yeah.
That sounds great.

41:16.542 --> 41:19.545
You know, actually, I have
to get to a Zoom, but...

41:19.578 --> 41:21.613
I'll see you around.

41:21.713 --> 41:24.149
Yeah.

41:36.027 --> 41:38.630
♪ Gotta live it up ♪

41:38.730 --> 41:41.399
♪ Gotta be strong ♪

41:41.567 --> 41:42.433
