41:43.569 --> 41:45.671
Good, right?

41:48.173 --> 41:50.842
Hello?

41:52.578 --> 41:55.180
You look so handsome.
You look like an accountant.

41:55.280 --> 41:57.649
Thank you. Thank you.

41:57.749 --> 42:00.952
Wait, are you guys going
out to lunch without me?

42:01.052 --> 42:03.321
You have far too many
cases to catch up on.

42:03.421 --> 42:05.156
Now, the ties, the socks,

42:05.256 --> 42:06.592
shirt and belt in that bag

42:06.692 --> 42:08.594
are more professional
than what you're wearing.

42:08.627 --> 42:10.596
We can take it out
of your first paycheck.

42:10.696 --> 42:12.297
And this is your bus pass,

42:12.397 --> 42:15.601
because you are not driving
that jalopy into this building.

42:15.667 --> 42:17.468
Okay? See you soon.

42:17.603 --> 42:19.137
Good luck.

